==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Canker blossom
<hw>Can"ker blos`som</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>That which blasts a blossom
as a canker does.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>O me! you juggler! you <qex>canker blossom</qex>!⟦br⟧
You thief of Love!</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cankered</ent>⟦br⟧
